{"tid":2225943,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"12名現時被中國扣押香港青年中，最少兩人有長期病患需要接受治療","createTime":"2020-10-01T16:31:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-01T17:19:34.000Z","uid":261647,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5ab6c473040e0f2ef345c285ebbf6779c2482bb8","tid":2225943,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T16:31:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/nostakemedicalstudent/photos/a.139689010748980/380884399962772/?type=3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fnostakemedicalstudent%2Fphotos%2Fa.139689010748980%2F380884399962772%2F%3Ftype%3D3&d=2MheXYw%2FBwPqfvV%2BE34w10pSq8GU1PbbWBdRLYKbGpc%3D&h=e0240e1a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/nostakemedicalstudent/photos/a.139689010748980/380884399962772/?type=3</a><br />\n<br />\n【 病人接受醫療嘅權利都被奪去，醫療界、香港人憑何沉默？ 】<br />\n<br />\n十二名現時被中國扣押嘅香港青年中，最少兩人有長期病患需要接受治療，但家屬卻不被容許為佢地送藥。接受治療權利係最最最基本嘅人權，但卻被中国嘅「陽光司法」所禁止。<br />\n<br />\n作為醫療界嘅一份子，抑或作為一個普通有良知嘅人都好，眼見病人嘅基本權利被中国當局肆意踐踏，實在冇可能作壁上觀。呢件事已經非關政治，係最基本不過嘅人道議題。目睹如斯不義卻沉默，只會成為欺壓者嘅幫兇。人命攸關，請各位站在十二位香港青年一邊，用各自嘅方法，去持續喚醒世界對佢地嘅關注。<br />\n<br />\n比多少少資訊大家，十二手足之一嘅喬映瑜，據報本身有嚴重抑鬱，正服用Pristiq 100mg。Pristiq呢隻SNRI，一般較少係抑鬱嘅第一線療法，現時常見用法係係第一線療法SSRI未夠有效後，先轉用Pristiq，而起始劑量多數係25-50mg，100mg亦係相當較高劑量，可見病情相信不算輕微。而長時間服用Pristiq，突然間冇得用藥，亦有超過50%病人會出現戒斷症候群，包括作嘔、肚瀉、頭痛、頭暈等等。<br />\n<br />\n（以下呢段字同呢幅圖，絕對歡迎大家隨便攞去唔同渠道如Twitter等廣傳，唔使問唔使Credits。）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QXFdrry.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQXFdrry.jpg&h=1c96b9c8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c279d28cc97f310388eb9e4d7a09094529579fe6","tid":2225943,"uid":291750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T16:36:28.000Z","msg":"不能忘記<br />\n<br />\n我唔覺得你地有幾想制裁中國囉<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2224228\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2224228</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"3fd1deeef0a5bdd5045dc66a2fda79878a4f28e3","tid":2225943,"uid":96327,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T16:36:47.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da2267af7b30c9df0ce6b25620739ece43fcf6bb","tid":2225943,"uid":63400,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T16:40:39.000Z","msg":"偷渡去台灣就夠精力？坐下監又話需要治療？畀啲勇氣喇香港人"},{"pid":"e60c95ad6af1b59c62deb122f93937dc7dd06c70","tid":2225943,"uid":96327,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"da2267af7b30c9df0ce6b25620739ece43fcf6bb","tid":2225943,"uid":63400,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T16:40:39.000Z","msg":"偷渡去台灣就夠精力？坐下監又話需要治療？畀啲勇氣喇香港人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T16:41:55.000Z","msg":"佢嗰陣都仲有藥"},{"pid":"da81a72d90e8c34ea60183ad4389d9b14e428f11","tid":2225943,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T16:43:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95c320ef58099b119d951516986e3a3d8796d959","tid":2225943,"uid":124983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"da2267af7b30c9df0ce6b25620739ece43fcf6bb","tid":2225943,"uid":63400,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T16:40:39.000Z","msg":"偷渡去台灣就夠精力？坐下監又話需要治療？畀啲勇氣喇香港人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T17:19:34.000Z","msg":"低級自爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}